# Mood of the Queue

A simple internal tool to track the emotional “vibe” of a support ticket queue throughout the day. Built with Streamlit, Google Sheets, and Plotly.


---

## 🔧 Features

- 😃 Log a mood using emojis
- 📝 Add optional notes
- 📤 Append to Google Sheet in real-time
- 📈 View mood counts for today in a dynamic bar chart

---

## 🚀 Live App 

🔗 [Streamlit App](<https://moodofthequeue-epjct6brhbezmgrwo4er3s.streamlit.app/>)  

